                <h1>About<span> Us</span></h1>
                <p>A Home Away from Home</p>
                <p>Backed by more than 40 years of related industry experience, the proprietors of Briarwood Manor are dedicated to becoming the area's premier name in personal care. We currently offer accommodations for 20 residents, if need be and can accommodate most residents with the convenience to age in place. Above all, we care about how our residents are treated and expect only the best from our staff.</p>
               <p><strong>Staff Qualifications</strong></p>
