                            <li>Criminal background check</li>
							<li>Drug screening</li>
                            <li style="width:100%;">Department of Public Welfare certified aide</li>
                            <li>Certified medication administrators</li>
                            <li>Certified in topical treatments</li>
                            <li>Certified Diabetes care givers</li>
                            <li>Certified in CPR/First Aid</li>
                            <li>Fire safety certified</li>
                            <li>On-going continuing education</li>
                            </ul>
